	<refsection id="bugs">
		<title>Bugs</title>

		<para><application>Lexi</application> currently silently permits
			several semantically nonsensical but syntactically valid
			constructs which result in undefined behaviour. These are
			described in
			<citetitle pubwork="article">The Lexi users' Guide</citetitle>.
			It is expected that in future versions of
			<application>Lexi</application> these will produce errors
			during compilation.</para>
	</refsection>
